36:41.621 --> 36:42.674
Ahh.

36:50.181 --> 36:51.963
Ahh.

36:56.435 --> 36:59.524
Mick, where the hell you been?

36:59.690 --> 37:00.882
Makin' us some money, Sean-O.

37:01.007 --> 37:02.152
Right this way, lads.

37:02.318 --> 37:06.114
You won't be disappointed, I promise.

37:18.023 --> 37:20.170
[Men grunting]

37:22.026 --> 37:24.007
Hey, hey, hey.
No shoving.

37:24.173 --> 37:25.338
One at a time.

37:25.463 --> 37:27.594
